
@startuml AdamW_Flowchart
title Flowchart Cara Kerja Optimizer AdamW (Per Iterasi)

start
:Ambil Batch Data Baru;
:Hitung Loss dan Gradient g_t;

' --- Adam Core ---
:Hitung Estimasi Momen 1 (m_t) dan 2 (v_t);
:Koreksi Bias Momen (m̂_t dan v̂_t);

' --- AdamW Pembaruan Decoupled ---
fork
  :Hitung Pembaruan Dasar Adam:
  \n$\Delta W_{Adam} = \eta \frac{\hat{m}_t}{\sqrt{\hat{v}_t} + \epsilon}$;
fork again
  :Hitung Weight Decay:
  \n$-\eta \cdot \lambda \cdot W_{t-1}$;
end fork

:Pembaruan Bobot Akhir:
\n$W_t = W_{t-1} - \Delta W_{Adam} - \eta \lambda W_{t-1}$;
stop
@enduml